    "superresolution.screen.config.options.tooltip.theme_contrast_level": "Adjust UI contrast (-1 = lowest, 0 = default, 1 = highest)",
    "superresolution.screen.config.options.tooltip.upscale_ratio": "Higher values lower in-game resolution, blur visuals, and reduce performance cost\nLower values raise in-game resolution, improve clarity and image quality, but increase performance cost\nCurrent rendering resolution: %sx%s\nCurrent rendering precision: %s\nRecommended range: 1.4~1.8",
